1)EC2 > launch instance > launch instance
2)after the vm status is "running", in left pannel: instances > instance ID > press the ID of the created vm
3)copy the "public ipv4 dns". press connect > rdp client.
4) in windows open "remote desktop connection" > paste the dns 
5) in rdp client page, choose username and press Get password, upload the private ,pem key > decreypt password. 
copy the password and add the credentials in remote desktop connection >

> connect > more choices > use a different account
